{"tid":1547583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］9月9樂富要人！！！","createTime":"2019-09-06T17:02:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T16:35:10.000Z","uid":195116,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ff999e105ca882dd1ff3e4fa270ed2de2788ea2f","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBJNYz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBJNYz8.jpg&h=9d79836b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">事件<span style=\"color: red;\">：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9月9樂富聯校人鏈</span></strong></span><br />\n發起人：樂富人<br />\n參與人：<span style=\"color: gold;\">余中、永光、扶輪、龍官及任何人</span>，黑色口罩為記<br />\n時間：9月9日7:00am-7:55am <br />\n衣著要求：無<br />\n地點路線：余中-&gt;富美街-&gt;鳳舞街-&gt;永光-&gt;天橋-&gt;馬仔坑路-&gt;龍官<br />\n￼<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eSNnNtk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeSNnNtk.jpg&h=92cdced4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n活動內容：築人鏈、叫口號、唱歌、舉牌<br />\n性質：<span style=\"color: red;\">和平及快閃</span>。本活動並沒有向popo申請，故此有可能被起訴非法集結。所以該活動著重絕對和平及迅速。<br />\n主題：守護香港核心價值，強調「五大訴求，缺一不可」，正視及追究警方濫權行為，譴責政府無能、包庇與民為敵的態度<br />\n<br />\n潛在風險：<br />\n 1. 秋後算賬<br />\n &bull; 參與人建議配備黑色口罩以免被人標記<br />\n 2. popo重防<br />\n &bull; 任何時候不能主動挑釁popo，此為和平及迅速的活動，不會造成社會困擾，旨在表達市民訴求。如popo主動出擊，所有人即散，前提是保護所有中學生到達安全地方<br />\n 3. 藍絲家長阻擾<br />\n &bull; 不與之爭執，更不會出現肢體碰撞，如對方主動挑釁，我方則靠人多聲大嚇走對方<br />\n 4. 不同意見人士產生的肢體衝撞<br />\n &bull; 同上<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">運作：<br />\n 1. 當日需有數名志願者在維持秩序，志願者可融入人鏈中亦可站在人鏈外，目的視察周圍環境、<span style=\"color: red;\">督促交通安全及保障參與人人生安全</span>。<br />\n 2. 建議參與人可自備手牌、口罩等物資，我地亦會派發少量予各位，但惟不能確保每人都可得到。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"b3108aef16434185be1b7134072bb9cd0cfdb801","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:03:08.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"889fea82a2611419b6a591ed93a36c3539462845","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:03:28.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"67d9016fac7770c6d87b0528396d4869a83b5a3f","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"6ccfdc857324eb2a0678577b714f3fbcee1b003b","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"77312360ec7562781dc3a60cdcc3b586c202183b","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:04:02.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"5c5b83d719fc294cf3ba62c8464478a25a4d37e5","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"ae32df43b06d5aa3706e62db96225a66a27a99bd","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"59c0d5d1d1ef7607b893d50494404f3b3b1e7117","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:04:36.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"25b4135f075cf9d2e11c27ae399e0bf51951f14a","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:04:46.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"aaea0bb3c51ad9df2fe05f4720853eed993ad8cf","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:04:59.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"c678e244c81e2db08ea9100b691ce2896c8b1d0b","tid":1547583,"uid":195116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:05:19.000Z","msg":"香港人，加油！"},{"pid":"46deb12bca11f9d1309b97b26d6ef60f379521e5","tid":1547583,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T17:07:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><spa